    "html": "<DOCUMENT>\n<TYPE>EX-99.1\n<SEQUENCE>2\n<FILENAME>d892700dex991.htm\n<DESCRIPTION>EX-99.1\n<TEXT>\n<HTML><HEAD>\n<TITLE>EX-99.1</TITLE>\n</HEAD>\n <BODY BGCOLOR=\"WHITE\">\n\n <P STYLE=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:ARIAL\" ALIGN=\"right\"><B>Exhibit 99.1 </B></P> <P STYLE=\"font-size:12pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">&nbsp;</P>\n<P STYLE=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">\n\n\n<IMG SRC=\"g892700ex99_1logo.jpg\" ALT=\"LOGO\">\n </P> <P STYLE=\"margin-top:24pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:16pt; font-family:ARIAL\"><FONT COLOR=\"#355b8c\">Notice of our 2015 annual meeting of shareholders </FONT></P>\n<P STYLE=\"margin-top:22pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:8.5pt; font-family:ARIAL\">You are invited to our 2015 annual meeting: </P> <P STYLE=\"margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:ARIAL\"><FONT COLOR=\"#355b8c\">When\n</FONT></P><DIV STYLE=\"position:relative;float:left; margin-right:1%; width:48%;padding-right:9pt;padding-bottom:8pt;overflow:hidden;padding-top:3pt\">\n <P STYLE=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:8.5pt; font-family:ARIAL\">Friday, May&nbsp;22, 2015 </P> <P STYLE=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:8.5pt; font-family:ARIAL\">10 a.m.\nCST </P> <P STYLE=\"margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:ARIAL\"><FONT COLOR=\"#355b8c\">Where </FONT></P> <P STYLE=\"margin-top:8pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:8.5pt; font-family:ARIAL\">Cameco Corporation </P>\n<P STYLE=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:8.5pt; font-family:ARIAL\">2121 - 11th Street West </P> <P STYLE=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:8.5pt; font-family:ARIAL\">Saskatoon, Saskatchewan </P>\n<P STYLE=\"margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:10pt; font-family:ARIAL\"><FONT COLOR=\"#355b8c\">Your vote is important </FONT></P> <P STYLE=\"margin-top:8pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:8.5pt; font-family:ARIAL\">If you held Cameco common\nshares on March&nbsp;24, 2015, you are entitled to receive notice of and to vote at this meeting. </P> <P STYLE=\"margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:8.5pt; font-family:ARIAL\">You can vote in person at the meeting or by proxy. </P>\n<P STYLE=\"margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:8.5pt; font-family:ARIAL\">See pages 5 through 10 of the attached management proxy circular for information about what the meeting will cover, who can vote and how to vote. </P>\n<P STYLE=\"margin-top:30pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:8.5pt; font-family:ARIAL\">By order of the board of directors, </P> <P STYLE=\"font-size:12pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">&nbsp;</P>\n<P STYLE=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt; margin-left:7pt\">\n\n\n<IMG SRC=\"g892700ex99_1sig.jpg\" ALT=\"LOGO\">\n </P> <P STYLE=\"margin-top:6pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:8.5pt; font-family:ARIAL\">Sean Quinn </P> <P STYLE=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:8.5pt; font-family:ARIAL\">Senior Vice-President, </P>\n<P STYLE=\"margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:8.5pt; font-family:ARIAL\">Chief Legal Officer and Corporate Secretary </P> <P STYLE=\"margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:8.5pt; font-family:ARIAL\">Saskatoon, Saskatchewan </P>\n<P STYLE=\"margin-top:12pt; margin-bottom:0pt; font-size:8.5pt; font-family:ARIAL\">April&nbsp;8, 2015\n</P></DIV><DIV STYLE=\"position:relative;float:right; width:48%;padding-right:9pt;padding-bottom:8pt;overflow:hidden;padding-top:3pt\">\n <P STYLE=\"font-size:2pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">&nbsp;</P>\n<TABLE CELLSPACING=\"0\" CELLPADDING=\"0\" WIDTH=\"100%\" BORDER=\"0\" STYLE=\"BORDER-COLLAPSE:COLLAPSE; font-family:ARIAL; font-size:10pt\" ALIGN=\"center\">\n\n\n<TR>\n<TD WIDTH=\"3%\"></TD>\n<TD VALIGN=\"bottom\" WIDTH=\"1%\"></TD>\n<TD WIDTH=\"3%\"></TD>\n<TD VALIGN=\"bottom\" WIDTH=\"1%\"></TD>\n<TD WIDTH=\"88%\"></TD>\n<TD VALIGN=\"bottom\" WIDTH=\"1%\"></TD>\n<TD WIDTH=\"3%\"></TD></TR>\n\n\n<TR STYLE=\"font-family:ARIAL; font-